| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4532 — Recovery Inhibition (nitrogen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7be67cdc-50b9-5e76-ad1c-a3e5be0ee684"
